        description: "Most UAE businesses have claimed their Google Business Profile but have not fully optimised it — missing services, uncategorised offerings, thin descriptions, and no keyword strategy in the business description. Google uses GBP completeness as a direct ranking signal for map pack positions. An incomplete profile is a significant competitive disadvantage that is straightforward to address.",
